  "statement": {
    "markdown": "## Responsive Table Challenge\n\n### Requirements\n1. Create a table with the following structure\n| Name | Age | Occupation |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| John | 25 | Developer |\n| Jane | 31 | Designer |\n| Bob | 42 | Manager |\n2. Make the table responsive, so it adapts to different screen sizes."
  },
  "constraints": [
    "Use Tailwind CSS classes for styling.",
    "Do not use any JavaScript files or libraries.",
    "The table must be fully functional on desktop and mobile devices."
  ],
  "referenceAssets": [],
  "starterCode": {
    "html": "<html>\n<head>\n    <link href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>\n    <title>Responsive Table</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class='container mx-auto p-4\">\n        <table>\n            <thead>\n                <tr>\n                    <th class='px-4 py-2'>Name</th>\n                    <th class='px-4 py-2'>Age</th>\n                    <th class='px-4 py-2'>Occupation</th>\n                </tr>\n            </thead>\n            <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                    <td class='border px-4 py-2'>John</td>\n                    <td class='border px-4 py-2'>25</td>\n                    <td class='border px-4 py-2'>Developer</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td class='border px-4 py-2'>Jane</td>\n                    <td class='border px-4 py-2'>31</td>\n                    <td class='border px-4 py-2'>Designer</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td class='border px-4 py-2'>Bob</td>\n                    <td class='border px-4 py-2'>42</td>\n                    <td class='border px-4 py-2'>Manager</td>\n                </tr>\n            </tbody>\n        </table>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
